January 04, 2018

To determine the HMS Momentum Correction:

Momentum Fraction:  DATA - SIMC

DATA = (Pcalc - Pmeas) / Pmeas
SIMC = (Pcalc - Pmeas) / Pmeas

If DATA > SIMC:
--> (Pcalc - Pmeas)_data > (Pcalc - Pmeas)_simc ---> Pmeas_data < Pmeas_simc
Pmeas_data_corr = Pmeas_data + Pmeas_data*(DATA-SIMC) = Pmeas_data (1 + (DATA-SIMC))   --> (DATA-SIMC) > 0

If DATA < SIMC:    
--> (Pcalc - Pmeas)_data < (Pcalc - Pmeas)_simc ---> Pmeas_data > Pmeas_simc         
Pmeas_data_corr = Pmeas_data + Pmeas_data*(DATA-SIMC) = Pmeas_data (1 + (DATA-SIMC)) --> (DATA-SIMC) < 0 

The values for DATA-SIMC are:
**(DATA -  SIMC)***
Run 3288: mean: -0.00221326 err: 4.31398e-05     
Run 3371: mean: 0.000497302 err: 4.22052e-05                                                                                                             
Run 3374: mean: -0.00165585 err: 5.18022e-05                                                                                                                
Run 3377: mean: -0.00131076 err: 6.43251e-05 

Correction Factor:
3288: 1 - 0.00221326  = 0.99778674  
3371: 1 + 0.000497302 = 1.0004973
3374: 1 - 0.00165585  = 0.99834415
3377: 1 - 0.00131076  = 0.99868924 

Fine Tune Corrected HMS Momentum:
3288: 2.9444540 * 0.99778674 = 2.9379372 
3371: 3.4772470 * 1.0004973  = 3.4789762
3374: 2.3160550 * 0.99834415 = 2.3122200
